      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FEARLESS BANDIT (8) was quickly out of the boxes with a slick early sectional clocking 29.56 with a 13 length win at Wentworth Park over 520m. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Great chance to get the job done again. FINE SHINE (1) was below best last time at Temora (25.65) in a NG, finishing a 5.5 lengths fifth. Has two wins already from this draw. Suited here and expected to run well. ALLERGY FREE (4) has been out of the placings at his last couple but on the winners' heels when placing three back (26.05) in a Grade 4/5 at Temora. Can improve sharply here. PAW ZEVA (2) showed great speed to lead all the way last start. Big chance again.",
